node.text: Ask us who our ultimate girl crush is, and we’ll answer with @devonleecarlson, each and every time. Whether it’s her carefree attitude or the endless good vibes she shared with her community - we couldn’t heart Devon more. Influenced by California-cool vibes 90’s nostalgia, DLCxLOC features three new styles. 📹 by @lilmami_lani ❤️‍🔥 all hats available now via link in bio ✨

node.title: Devon Lee Carlson x Lack of Color

node.text: Shot on location in Australia by Rob Tilbury. Come and get lost in the fondness of yesteryear and reflect on a time gone by, while looking towards a new way forward, with LOC’s new Revolution range.
